item.description:
Suzuki's Blog https://kanajin.github.io/datastructure/bubblesort/ -<h1 id="冒泡排序">冒泡排序</h1>
<p>逐步比较相邻的两个数，如果前一个比后一个大，就对调他们的位置。</p>
<h2 id="内循环">内循环：</h2>
<p>遍历一次数组，比较a[n]与a[n+1]的大小，根据情况执行对调，然后n+1，重复</p>
<h2 id="外循环">外循环：</h2>
<p>需要遍历几次数组（执行几次内循环）才可以完成冒泡排序。值为数组长度（上界）</p>
<h2 id="代码">代码：</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-C" data-lang="C"><span style="color:#66d9ef">void</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">sort</span>(<span style="color:#66d9ef">int</span> <span style="color:#f92672">*</span>a, <span style="color:#66d9ef">int</span> size){
<span style="color:#66d9ef">for</span>(<span style="color:#66d9ef">int</span> j <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#ae81ff">0</span>; j <span style="color:#f92672">&lt;</span> size <span style="color:#f92672">-</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span>; j<span style="color:#f92672">++</span>){
<span style="color:#66d9ef">for</span>(<span style="color:#66d9ef">int</span> i <span style="color:#f92672">=</span> <span style="color:#ae81ff">0</span>; i <span style="color:#f92672">&lt;</span> size <span style="color:#f92672">-</span> <span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span>; i<span style="color:#f92672">++</span>){
<span style="color:#66d9ef">if</span>(a[i] <span style="color:#f92672">&gt;</span> a[i <span style="color:#f92672">+</span> <span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span>]){
swap(a <span style="color:#f92672">+</span> i, a <span style="color:#f92672">+</span> i <span style="color:#f92672">+</span> <span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span>);
}
}
}
}
</code></pre></div>- https://kanajin.github.io/datastructure/bubblesort/ -
